data.description: Just 6 yrs old and plenty of space to enjoy good living. When you enter the grand foyer is spacious and presents a view of the home that is spectacular. This 3 bedroom house has an 4th room that is currently a bedroom but can be converted to an office or den. The kitchen is open to family room for continue family connection. The large master suite is very private with large bedroom, walk in closets and en-suite. The home offers a separate dining room not seen in the new models today. This home has a very large backyard that is fenced all around. One of the best features is it has Solar panels, walk into instant savings . This home is well maintained and ready to move in. Don't miss out on this great home for the family.
